Local government

   Sign up for updates to this topic page

On this page

    1. Services
    2. Guidance and regulation
    3. News and communications
    4. Research and statistics
    5. Policy papers and consultations
    6. Transparency and freedom of information releases
    7. Organisations
    8. Explore sub-topics

Services

    1. Check your Council Tax band
       Find out the Council Tax band for a property in England, Scotland
       or Wales by looking up the property's postcode online
    2. Find and check your business rates valuation
       How to check the rateable value of your business property - compare
       it with other properties, request changes to your valuation and
       challenge the business rates you've been charged
    3. Pay your Council Tax
       Pay Council Tax online or by other methods, like direct debit to
       your local council
    4. Council Tax
       Your Council Tax bill - how to work it out, who has to pay,
       discounts and exemptions for students and disabled people, second
       homes, empty properties, paying the bill
    5. Apply for Council Tax Reduction
       Apply to your local council for Council Tax Reduction if you're on
       a low income or benefits - this has replaced Council Tax Benefit

   See more services in this topic

